---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { absoluteUrl } from "../lib/site";

const canonicalUrl = absoluteUrl("/contact/");
const alternateEsUrl = absoluteUrl("/es/contact/");
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact | Visit Korea Planner"
  description="How to contact PlanMyKorea for questions, corrections, and partnership inquiries."
  bodyClass="page--leaf"
  canonicalUrl={canonicalUrl}
  alternateEnUrl={canonicalUrl}
  alternateEsUrl={alternateEsUrl}
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <h1>Contact</h1>

    <p>Thank you for visiting PlanMyKorea.</p>

    <p>
      If you have questions about our content, notice outdated information, or
      want to reach us for collaboration inquiries, please use the contact
      details below.
    </p>

    <h2>1) General Questions (About the content)</h2>
    <p>For general questions related to information on this website:</p>
    <p>Email: bayernmc@gmail.com</p>
    <p>
      Please note: PlanMyKorea provides general travel information only. We may
      not be able to provide personalized trip planning, visa consultation, or
      individual immigration advice.
    </p>

    <h2>2) Report an Error / Outdated Information</h2>
    <p>If you find a factual error or outdated details, we appreciate your help.</p>
    <p>When reporting an issue, please include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The page URL</li>
      <li>The section or sentence that needs updating</li>
      <li>The source for the correction (official link if available)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If verified, we will update the page when appropriate.</p>

    <h2>3) Business / Partnership Inquiries</h2>
    <p>For media, collaboration, or partnership inquiries:</p>
    <p>Email: bayernmc@gmail.com</p>
    <p>
      Any sponsored or paid placements (if accepted) will be clearly disclosed.
    </p>

    <h2>Important Notice</h2>
    <p>
      PlanMyKorea is an independent travel information website and is not
      affiliated with the Korean government, immigration authorities, airlines,
      airports, or other official organizations.
    </p>
    <p>
      We cannot make decisions regarding visas, entry approval, or official
      documentation. For urgent immigration or visa matters, please contact the
      relevant government authority directly.
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Any information you send by email will be used only to respond to your
      inquiry.
    </p>
    <p>
      Please do not send sensitive personal information (e.g., passport
      numbers, payment details, or government IDs).
    </p>
    <p>
      For more details, please review our
      <a href="https://planmykorea.com/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 10px 0 24px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }

  .legal-page h2 {
    margin: 24px 0 10px;
  }

  .legal-page p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .legal-page ul {
    margin: 0 0 12px 20px;
    padding: 0;
  }
</style>
